PrecisAmendment to Order in Council P.C. 1989-3/2182, as amended, that will authorize the EXPORT DEVELOPMENT CORPORATION to enter into insurance contracts in order to provide Canadian exporters with insurance against prior and post-shipment risks arising from or associated with the sale of various agricultural commodities to CUBA in the 1993 calendar year.
Attachments
precis:
Amendment to Order in Council P.C. 1989-3/2182, as amended, that will
authorize the EXPORT DEVELOPMENT CORPORATION to enter into insurance
contracts in order to provide Canadian exporters with insurance against
prior and post-shipment risks arising from or associated with the sale of
various agricultural commodities to CUBA in the 1993 calendar year.
